    "body": "### Problem\n\nApparently `cmd: string[]` does not use the discovered `root_dir` as its CWD. That seems like an oversight?\n\nExample: https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/pull/4456\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nUse root_dir as the CWD when invoking the `cmd: string[]`.\n\ncc @neovim/lsp ",
